1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:33,340
The speaker quotes Scripture, tells stories, and uses proper punctuation, capitalization, and complete sentences.

2
00:00:33,360 --> 00:00:42,060
Restrictive barriers are not those of just the body, but of the mind and the spirit.

3
00:00:42,380 --> 00:00:52,590
My old boss used to say to me, the greatest barrier, Kirk, to success is between your ears.

4
00:00:54,660 --> 00:00:55,240
He was right.

5
00:00:56,670 --> 00:01:05,930
As I struggled making cold calls in that first business venture, the greatest barrier was not anything but between my own ears.

6
00:01:07,170 --> 00:01:08,990
Did I walk in a winner that morning?

7
00:01:09,090 --> 00:01:11,190
Did I walk in a loser afraid of the phone?

8
00:01:12,480 --> 00:01:14,320
And I battled back and forth.

9
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:17,540
It was between the ears, in the heart and the spirit.

10
00:01:19,420 --> 00:01:23,160
Many of you know that I'm a big fan of Walt Disney and Disneyland.

11
00:01:23,360 --> 00:01:24,380
That's no secret.

12
00:01:24,860 --> 00:01:30,800
Ever since I was little, the Magic Kingdom just had sway over my heart.

13
00:01:31,540 --> 00:01:36,080
And every few years, I had the privilege of driving down the back of that station wagon

14
00:01:36,080 --> 00:01:41,800
all the way to Disneyland and I just love that place and as you know I try and get there as

15
00:01:41,800 --> 00:01:48,330
often as possible to enjoy a day with my kids in the happiest place on earth but not only is

16
00:01:48,330 --> 00:01:54,510
Disneyland this wonderful theme park and escapist attraction I am fascinated with Disneyland

17
00:01:54,510 --> 00:02:03,650
because it's an amazing dream of a gentleman with a vision and I am fascinated by the place

18
00:02:03,650 --> 00:02:09,430
and by Walt Disney, who could see this place, this kingdom, in his mind

19
00:02:09,430 --> 00:02:12,440
and how it has come to reality.

20
00:02:14,100 --> 00:02:17,440
If you go in the gallery above the Pirates of the Caribbean,

21
00:02:17,780 --> 00:02:18,580
you know where this is?

22
00:02:19,060 --> 00:02:21,600
If you go into that gallery up the stairs,

23
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:25,600
you get a chance to walk amongst the artist's conception,

24
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:29,820
the drawings and the pictures of the early ideas

25
00:02:29,820 --> 00:02:32,060
as they began to lay them out on paper.

26
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:41,000
And I love to see how certain rides took shape as a dream, then to paper, and then into reality.

27
00:02:42,420 --> 00:02:45,700
In fact, in the early drawings, the train actually went the other way.

28
00:02:45,780 --> 00:02:46,440
Did you know that?

29
00:02:47,990 --> 00:02:51,490
And somewhere they set it right, and it goes the direction it goes today.

30
00:02:52,860 --> 00:02:57,000
Walt Disney once said, if you can dream it, you can do it.

31
00:02:58,100 --> 00:03:04,120
And I'm inspired every time I walk down that center alleyway there with all the buildings,

32
00:03:04,300 --> 00:03:06,060
in the Disneyland castle in front of me,

33
00:03:06,140 --> 00:03:08,260
I say, you can dream it, you can do it.

34
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:11,190
What a testimony of dreams

35
00:03:11,190 --> 00:03:13,200
and of achievement

36
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:15,260
coming out of the depths of our spirit.

37
00:03:16,300 --> 00:03:18,400
Have you ever had a dream in your life?

38
00:03:19,580 --> 00:03:22,300
Have you ever allowed your sanctified imagination

39
00:03:22,300 --> 00:03:25,180
to dream what God might do

40
00:03:25,180 --> 00:03:27,240
in and through your life?

41
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:31,740
If you're a believer in Jesus Christ,

42
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:34,860
I believe the Holy Spirit longs

43
00:03:34,860 --> 00:03:37,420
to give you a dream of a better future.

44
00:03:39,700 --> 00:03:41,420
Perhaps your dream involves

45
00:03:41,420 --> 00:03:44,100
using your God-given spiritual gifts

46
00:03:44,100 --> 00:03:47,080
to serve Christ and others in a passionate way.

47
00:03:48,190 --> 00:03:49,930
Perhaps you've dreamed of being part

48
00:03:49,930 --> 00:03:52,030
