49
00:03:52,030 --> 00:03:54,630
that's empowered by the Holy Spirit.

50
00:03:56,130 --> 00:03:58,750
Perhaps your dream involves sharing Christ

51
00:03:58,750 --> 00:04:01,670
in the marketplace and seeing people you know

52
00:04:01,670 --> 00:04:04,930
